{"tid":1652993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美心食肆全遭蹂躪 塗鴉爆窗碗碟滿地","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T02:25:57.000Z","uid":56881,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dec573f03768b9c0b18c24e6d6f185b1afbcd018","tid":1652993,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%85%A8%E9%81%AD%E8%B9%82%E8%BA%AA-%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89%E7%88%86%E7%AA%97%E7%A2%97%E7%A2%9F%E6%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0-214500767.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B9%2582%25E8%25BA%25AA-%25E5%25A1%2597%25E9%25B4%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AA%2597%25E7%25A2%2597%25E7%25A2%259F%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%259C%25B0-214500767.html&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeNzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=28f345a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%85%A8%E9%81%AD%E8%B9%82%E8%BA%AA-%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89%E7%88%86%E7%AA%97%E7%A2%97%E7%A2%9F%E6%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0-214500767.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gsmlnibOgvo5zGFoVKEiMQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/8ed05fcecc9e3ab4b32fd6f872582efa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgsmlnibOgvo5zGFoVKEiMQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F8ed05fcecc9e3ab4b32fd6f872582efa&h=8c5cab53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美心旗下食肆玻璃遭嚴重破壞。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】示威者昨在多個商場針對部分目標店舖進行破壞，當中美心集團旗下店舖最慘烈，旗下的美心西餅、餐廳及酒樓，以及有份經營的星巴克、元氣壽司、丼丼屋及魚尚等，全部無一幸免。當中位於沙田新城市廣場的餐廳「潮庭」經示威者大肆蹂躪後「甩皮甩骨」，牆上被塗鴉、桌椅東歪西倒，碗碟碎滿一地，所有玻璃物體亦告粉碎，慘不忍睹。<br />\n<br />\n福建人經營的「優品360」零食店是示威者首選攻擊目標之一，多個分店被破壞，閘門被強行撬開，零食散滿一地，有部分食物包裝更疑遭放火燃燒，幸火勢不大未有蔓延。示威者搗亂後於店舖外牆塗鴉，寫上「奶共」、「福建幫殺人償命」等字句。美心集團旗下的餐廳，其桌椅更被人搬到店外，在商場及馬路上作為路障。<br />\n<br />\n逛街遇示威 內地自由行慌逃<br />\n<br />\n位於沙田的電訊設備商華為專門店損毀慘重，其閘門是橫向式拉閘，輕易就被示威者撬開，展示櫃及大型桌子被推倒，所有玻璃均被打碎。沙田的中國銀行自助櫃員機亦遭到示威者毀壞。由於是周日，沙田新城市廣場仍有不少內地自由行拖住行李箱逛街，遇到示威者暴力破壞行動後，均嚇至雞飛狗走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1SanAKxRnQS7rdeS37peTA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/e1f2c09eaf5b0d0199d1c90dcdf22629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1SanAKxRnQS7rdeS37peTA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fe1f2c09eaf5b0d0199d1c90dcdf22629&h=dfddbd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為專門店閘門被暴徒強行撬開入內大搗亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vn4jE4TdrF3swQxVxIvnvQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/3a397892df00ab7c6e3bb594b3004b1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVn4jE4TdrF3swQxVxIvnvQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F3a397892df00ab7c6e3bb594b3004b1a&h=34b254a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多間「優品360」零食店被塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n大小姐做咩要干預內政呢<br />\n勾結外國勢力唔好呀<br />\n美心幾時出黎再割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a538b7d81e4afb84e941c276cf9b58cad69217","tid":1652993,"uid":5822,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"睇張360圖 <br />\n但噴光復香港時代革命真係多餘 <br />\n直接屌你老母福建佬/黑社會360 仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a41f8de7ac2e946ccd7861fe6956cdec9559a1d","tid":1652993,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"in capitol we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk